dreisoft.tresos.launcher2.api.project
Class Project

java.lang.Object
  dreisoft.tresos.launcher2.api.project.Project

public class Project
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides access to tresos Studio projects, e.g. to call the generators of a project. Instances of this class are singletons of a certain tresos Studio project.

Since:
12.1
